Updated on 3/25/24: My name is Jonathan and I am a Turo POWER HOST born and raised in Orlando, FL. Prior to the pandemic, I was a live sound engineer. I want to ensure each guest has a memorable trip in a safe and clean vehicle. I make it easy by offering delivery as an option to all Orlando airports and more! I’m available 24/7 in English and Spanish, standing by for your request!

I am an automobile enthusiast with a taste for entrepreneurship.  Turo gives me the ability to own a fleet of amazing vehicles, for myself, and others to enjoy.

Enjoy the drive.

Connect on the Road: Feel free to ask me anything about the vehicles or recommendations for your trip during the booking process. I can't wait to connect and help you hit the road in style!
